{"tid":577301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[once...] 批中國製安全套太小　津巴布韋部長籲自家生產","createTime":"2018-03-01T15:43:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-01T16:18:45.000Z","uid":119393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1bbd3901a13cc6e37a88c72a4a453fa900d9e2d0","tid":577301,"uid":119393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T15:43:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180301/s00005/1519909521830\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180301%2Fs00005%2F1519909521830&d=vblYqEDm6m1M7u%2BEIZCfugRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=64033d19\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180301%2Fs00005%2F1519909521830&h=8e7cf0ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180301/s00005/1519909521830</a><br />\n<br />\n「中國製造」商品遍布全球，但總不可能每款商品都受別國歡迎。津巴布韋衛生部長David Parirenyatwa就表示，中國製安全套太小了，津巴布韋男士不合用，希望當地商人根據國民尺寸自行生產。<br />\n<br />\n他在首都哈拉雷一個論壇上提到，津巴布韋南部地區愛滋病疫情嚴重，因此衛生部正向當地男女推廣使用安全套，避免HIV蔓延。然而當地安全套大多來自中國，不少男性抱怨尺寸太小，似乎有必要盡快推出自家生產的安全套。<br />\n<br />\n2016年，當局向津巴布韋人們派發超過1.09億個安全套，平均每個國民分到33個，但愛滋病疫情依然嚴重，同年愛滋病感染人數高達130萬人。<br />\n<br />\n（New Zimbabwe）"},{"pid":"dcd2fef79fa4710ccace2cdf58eba322f2c87154","tid":577301,"uid":124689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T15:52:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae1ceb74853ad22dfbf2329e028e91c2b8b5bac6","tid":577301,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T15:54:41.000Z","msg":"小妹想試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1db3b9218efb6e8a2b2471efdf4d5abe082fc747","tid":577301,"uid":157535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T16:18:45.000Z","msg":"辛苦曬呀非洲嘅人<br />\n佢地扑野比個condom夾到實一實一定好辛苦，扑野都扑到唔舒服<br />\n<br />\n但係總統係咪自己試過?<br />\n有深刻體驗過先會發大黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}